Insider Activity


Individual




Gary K. Willis



Mr. Gary K. Willis is Chief Executive Officer at Zygo Corp., Independent Director at Plug Power, Inc., and Independent Director at Rofin-Sinar Technologies, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Plug Power, Inc., Rofin-Sinar Technologies, Inc., and Middlesex Health Services, Inc.
Mr. Willis was previously employed as Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer by The Foxboro Co. He also served on the board at Vion Pharmaceuticals, Inc. and Benthos, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Worcester Polytechnic Institute.



